        <Parent_String>ester [300015257], oxygenated solvent [300111664], solvent by composition or origin [300111667], solvent [300015217], materials by function [300014692], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
